{"id":145138,"type":6,"name":"きらきら研修医","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/c9/3b/145138_2449l.jpg","summary":"　　2007年1月11日开始的TBS系「亮闪的进修医生」周四晚10点播出。这是一部医疗喜剧，小西饰演的人物与到现在的印象有差异，是一位笨拙的进修 医生。而片中对小西有爱慕之心的护士角色，起用了WaT的瑛士(21)，真是一新鲜的阵容。制作人川西琢制片人认为「由于进修医生这个设定很新鲜，即未经世 故。小西具有这种物质，不需要过多的表演」。以往的医疗电视剧里主要倾向于天才外科医生及院内的政权争夺，本片却是以笨拙的主人公克服注射，止血工作等的的奋斗喜剧。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>闪亮的进修医生</li><li><span>配角: </span><a href=\"/person/19340\">桐谷美玲</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>灿烂研修医</li><li><span>集数: </span>11</li><li><span>开始: </span>2007-01-11</li><li><span>导演: </span>今井夏木 / 森永恭朗</li><li><span>编剧: </span>荒井修子 / 徳永友一</li><li><span>类型: </span>剧情 / 喜剧</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>日本</li><li><span>语言: </span>日语</li><li><span>每集长: </span>45m</li><li><span>主演: </span>小西真奈美 / ウエンツ瑛士 / 加藤雅也 / 原田芳雄</li><li><span>官方网站: </span>http://www.tbs.co.jp/kirakira-usako/</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt0997310</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"日本ドラマ","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":562596,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/562596","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":562597,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/562597","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":562598,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/562598","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":562599,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/562599","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":562600,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/562600","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":562601,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/562601","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":562602,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/562602","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"